Type of Feat: General
Prerequisite: Improved Unarmed Strike, base attack bonus +3.
Specifics: You deal more damage with your unarmed strikes.  At 3rd level you deal an extra 1d4 damage.  At 4th-7th, 1d6.  At 8th-11th, 1d8.  At 12th-15th, 1d10.  At 16th-20th, 2d6.

Use: Automatic.

Special: If you are a monk, you instead deal unarmed damage as a monk four levels higher.
